Identification of item,  date (if known); Gary Ware Collection of Martin Wong Letters; MSS 299; box number; folder number; Fales Library and Special Collections, New York University Libraries.
This collection consists of letters written by Martin Wong to Gary Ware from 1962 to 1975. The letters range in topic from personal affairs to California counterculture to art production.
